=== Aliases ===
If you found yourself using equery all the time to check USE flags, package files... you could write down a few handy aliases with `eq' as a prefix and the letter used by a function. I use `~/.aliasrc' for [[bash]] which could be used for any shell and `~/.oh-my-zsh/lib/aliases.zsh' for [[zsh]] because I use [https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh oh-my-zsh].

{{File|~/.aliasrc||<pre>
alias eqf='equery f'
alias equ='equery u'
alias eqh='equery h'
alias eqa='equery a'
alias eqb='equery b'
alias eql='equery l'
alias eqd='equery d'
alias eqg='equery g'
alias eqc='equery c'
alias eqk='equery k'
alias eqm='equery m'</pre>}}

